<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
      a {
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: small;
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 4px 8px;
        color: aliceblue;
        background-color: rgb(201, 47, 47);
      }
      a:hover {
        background-color: blue;
      }
      table {
        width: 600px;
      }
      tr:hover {
        background-color: rgb(97, 250, 130);
      }
      th {
        background-color: rgb(105, 23, 182);
        color: aliceblue;
      }
      th,
      td {
        padding: 5px;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Home Page</h1>
    <a href="/lectures">Lecturers</a>
    <a href="/students">Students</a>
    <!-- <a href="/lectures/delete/8">deleter</a> -->
    <hr />
    <h3>Students Page</h3>
    <p>
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Distinctio alias nulla modi? Saepe asperiores ratione quia a iure odit quasi animi recusandae, laudantium expedita accusamus natus deserunt vero at repudiandae facilis non
      tenetur maxime dolor fugiat voluptatibus rem assumenda autem. Porro at nisi veniam voluptate?
    </p>

    <div>
      <table border="1" cellspacing="0">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>id</th>
            <th>name</th>
            <th>major</th>
            <th>semester</th>
            <th>city</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <% students.forEach(student => { %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= student.id %></td>
            <td><%= student.name %></td>
            <td><%= student.major %></td>
            <td><%= student.semester %></td>
            <td><%= student.city %></td>
          </tr>
          <% }) %>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <hr />
    </div>
    <a href="/">Back Home</a>
  </body>
</html>
